snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: In Real Time | Interactive Demo Showcase
snippet.description: Welcome to the Five Nights at Freddy's: In Real Time | Interactive Demo. This is a showcase of our current work, but in an interactable form here on YouTube! Click on the prompted videos to explore gameplay, mechanics, animations, ambience, story and more.
